### Step 2: Add sample test file

Create a new file at `sdk/dnsresolver/Azure.ResourceManager.DnsResolver/tests/Samples/Sample1_DnsResolver.cs` using this template (fill in real subscription/resource IDs with test-framework equivalents from `DnsResolverTestBase`):

```csharp
// Copyright (c) Microsoft Corporation. All rights reserved.
