### Step 4: Validate

Run these commands in order from the repository root:

1. `dotnet build sdk/dnsresolver/Azure.ResourceManager.DnsResolver/`
2. `dotnet test sdk/dnsresolver/Azure.ResourceManager.DnsResolver/ --filter TestCategory!=Live`
3. `eng/scripts/Update-Snippets.ps1 dnsresolver` — injects code from `#region Snippet:` tags into README placeholders; check `git diff` to confirm README was updated
4. `eng/scripts/Export-API.ps1 dnsresolver` — regenerates public API listing files (no public types changed, but run to confirm no drift)
5. `dotnet format sdk/dnsresolver/Azure.ResourceManager.DnsResolver/`

